subsection.p:
Beginning with an initial state \xvec_0, we would like to know how the state evolves over time. For instance,
\begin{aligned} \xvec_1 \amp = T(\xvec_0)=A\xvec_0 \\ \xvec_2 \amp = T(\xvec_1) = (T\circ T)(\xvec_0)= A^2\xvec_0 \\ \xvec_3 \amp = T(\xvec_2) = A^3\xvec_0 \end{aligned}
and so on.
